products.name: Quiet Mind for Kids
products.description: What we think, say, see, hear, and experience all play a role in the conditioning of our mind – especially in our youth. How we speak to our children becomes their self-talk and identity. With this in mind, parents, coaches, and teachers – we will guide you through the steps to improve your child’s self-awareness, focus, and overall well-being. If we can teach them these mental skills now, the sky's the limit! Let’s not wait for a problem, but instead be PROACTIVE with their mindset and mental fitness.
